{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_160","type":"agent_message","text":"The new harness exposed the real remaining gap: Spring Boot sorts `IntegrationAutoConfiguration` by reading its class metadata before `ConfigurationClassParser` runs, so the existing conditional resource registration is too late. I’m making the integration autoconfigure class resources unconditional, which matches how the sibling Boot metadata is written."}}
